  "summary": "What's Changed Bump version to v1.129.0 by @mozzius in #11175 Add moduleSuffixes to tsconfig by @mozzius in #11146 Cache main bundle stats for PR checks by @mozzius in #11172 Reduce bottom hitslop for menu button by @ds-boyce in #11189 Split mobile build/submit pipelines and de-duplicate OTA workflow by @mozzius in #11133 Fix Android release asset upload by…",
  "content": "<h2>What&#x27;s Changed</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Bump version to v1.129.0 by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11175\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11175</a></li>\n<li>Add moduleSuffixes to tsconfig by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11146\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11146</a></li>\n<li>Cache main bundle stats for PR checks by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11172\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11172</a></li>\n<li>Reduce bottom hitslop for menu button by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11189\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11189</a></li>\n<li>Split mobile build/submit pipelines and de-duplicate OTA workflow by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11133\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11133</a></li>\n<li>Fix Android release asset upload by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11174\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11174</a></li>\n<li>Add nightly Maestro E2E workflow by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11181\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11181</a></li>\n<li>Lighten blue (link) text for dim and dark themes by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11164\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11164</a></li>\n<li>Stop closing search suggestions on input blur by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11199\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11199</a></li>\n<li>Add height constraint to full-height bottom sheets by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11178\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11178</a></li>\n<li>Fix image crop in quote posts, remove <code>PostEmbedViewContext.FeedEmbedRecordWithMedia</code> by <a href=\"https://github.com/estrattonbailey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@estrattonbailey</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11205\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11205</a></li>\n<li>Don&#x27;t roll up account labels into additional post alerts by <a href=\"https://github.com/estrattonbailey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@estrattonbailey</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11204\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11204</a></li>\n<li>Fix image menu in landscape orientation by <a href=\"https://github.com/vineyardbovines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@vineyardbovines</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11188\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11188</a></li>\n<li>Bump actions/setup-node from 6.4.0 to 7.0.0 by <a href=\"https://github.com/dependabot\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@dependabot</a>[bot] in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11203\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11203</a></li>\n<li>Bump the actions group with 4 updates by <a href=\"https://github.com/dependabot\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@dependabot</a>[bot] in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11202\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11202</a></li>\n<li>Restore activity notification subscriptions screen by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11201\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11201</a></li>\n<li>TypeScript 7 (attempt 2) by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11169\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11169</a></li>\n<li>add client event for failed video playback by <a href=\"https://github.com/vineyardbovines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@vineyardbovines</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11170\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11170</a></li>\n<li>Add new search results tab for starter packs by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11226\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11226</a></li>\n<li>Remove console.log, address lint by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11228\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11228</a></li>\n<li>Squish separate imports from the same source in ActivityNotificationSettings by <a href=\"https://github.com/RetroSunstar\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@RetroSunstar</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11225\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11225</a></li>\n<li>Move known likers below stats row; restore original order in stats row by <a href=\"https://github.com/abenzer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@abenzer</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11192\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11192</a></li>\n<li>Hide video pillarboxing on web when the card fits by <a href=\"https://github.com/vineyardbovines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@vineyardbovines</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11118\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11118</a></li>\n<li>Use stable tsgolint by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11229\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11229</a></li>\n<li>Pass recId with trending topic click metrics by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11232\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11232</a></li>\n<li>Add feature gate for starter pack search by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11234\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11234</a></li>\n<li>Update presentation of trending topics in Explore by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11227\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11227</a></li>\n<li>Create new trending feeds interstitial by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11207\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11207</a></li>\n<li>Update presentation of trending feeds by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11206\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11206</a></li>\n<li>Tweak loading state for block dialog by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11236\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11236</a></li>\n<li>Add From: Me to advanced search filters by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11126\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11126</a></li>\n<li>Display beta badge when isBetaUser is true by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11160\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11160</a></li>\n<li>Enable sharing a post to a new group chat by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11191\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11191</a></li>\n<li>React Native New Arch by <a href=\"https://github.com/abulenok\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@abulenok</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10980\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10980</a></li>\n<li>Sort follows and following behind gate by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11237\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11237</a></li>\n<li>Stub RN codegen native component on web by <a href=\"https://github.com/vineyardbovines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@vineyardbovines</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11240\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11240</a></li>\n<li>Display post counts greater than 1,000 by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11242\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11242</a></li>\n<li>Fix scroll forwarder web entrypoint by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11245\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11245</a></li>\n<li>Update API package and filter AA configs by platform by <a href=\"https://github.com/estrattonbailey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@estrattonbailey</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11244\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11244</a></li>\n<li>Migrate <code>useScrollViewOffset</code> to <code>useScrollOffset</code> by <a href=\"https://github.com/tomekzaw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@tomekzaw</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11250\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11250</a></li>\n<li>Tweak appearance of trending topics by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11253\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11253</a></li>\n<li>Fix Maestro E2E runtime environment by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11247\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11247</a></li>\n<li>Fix Maestro E2E regressions on iOS and Android by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11258\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11258</a></li>\n<li>Bump github.com/hashicorp/go-retryablehttp from 0.7.5 to 0.7.7 in /bskyweb by <a href=\"https://github.com/dependabot\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@dependabot</a>[bot] in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11257\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11257</a></li>\n<li>Add intl note on OTA flow by <a href=\"https://github.com/estrattonbailey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@estrattonbailey</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11241\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11241</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>New Contributors</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/abulenok\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@abulenok</a> made their first contribution in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10980\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10980</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/tomekzaw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@tomekzaw</a> made their first contribution in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11250\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11250</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Full Changelog</strong>: <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/compare/1.128.0...1.129.0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">1.128.0...1.129.0</a></p>",
